{"id":3563,"date":"2026-06-05T09:40:49","date_gmt":"2026-06-05T09:40:49","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/rabimbox.si\/?p=3563"},"modified":"2026-06-10T07:21:39","modified_gmt":"2026-06-10T07:21:39","slug":"kontrolni-seznam-za-selitev-kako-organizirati-selitev-brez-stresa-v-30-dneh","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/rabimbox.si\/en\/kontrolni-seznam-za-selitev-kako-organizirati-selitev-brez-stresa-v-30-dneh\/","title":{"rendered":"Moving Checklist: How to Organize a Stress-Free Move in 30 Days"},"content":{"rendered":"<div data-elementor-type=\"wp-post\" data-elementor-id=\"3563\" class=\"elementor elementor-3563\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-56c24e77 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"56c24e77\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-2ba22721 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"2ba22721\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"https:\/\/rabimbox.si\/en\/izposoja\/\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"225\" height=\"300\" src=\"https:\/\/rabimbox.si\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/08\/49823f1b-6f2c-4471-9154-023eca57e1fd-225x300.png\" class=\"attachment-medium size-medium wp-image-2273\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/rabimbox.si\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/08\/49823f1b-6f2c-4471-9154-023eca57e1fd-225x300.png 225w, https:\/\/rabimbox.si\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/08\/49823f1b-6f2c-4471-9154-023eca57e1fd-600x800.png 600w, https:\/\/rabimbox.si\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/08\/49823f1b-6f2c-4471-9154-023eca57e1fd-768x1024.png 768w, https:\/\/rabimbox.si\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/08\/49823f1b-6f2c-4471-9154-023eca57e1fd-1152x1536.png 1152w, https:\/\/rabimbox.si\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/08\/49823f1b-6f2c-4471-9154-023eca57e1fd-1536x2048.png 1536w, https:\/\/rabimbox.si\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/08\/49823f1b-6f2c-4471-9154-023eca57e1fd-scaled.png 1920w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 225px) 100vw, 225px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/a>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-5489180 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"5489180\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-271215dd elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"271215dd\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\"><a href=\"https:\/\/rabimbox.si\/en\/izposoja\/\">Moving Checklist: How to Organize a Stress-Free Move in 30 Days<\/a><\/h3>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-32b2f3b6 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"32b2f3b6\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-69cbe9a2 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"69cbe9a2\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p data-path-to-node=\"5\">Every apartment move brings a mix of excitement and that well-known feeling of dread when you look around and realize how many things you actually own. Without a proper plan, it is easy to find yourself frantically stuffing random items into flimsy cardboard boxes the night before the move.<\/p><p data-path-to-node=\"5\">\u00a0<\/p><p data-path-to-node=\"5\">To avoid this, we have prepared a complete moving checklist, broken down week by week. With this plan, your move will go smoothly, orderly, and without unnecessary stress.<\/p><p data-path-to-node=\"5\">\u00a0<\/p><p data-path-to-node=\"5\"><strong>4 weeks before the move: Time for a deep clean<\/strong><\/p><p data-path-to-node=\"8\">\u2022 Declutter (sorting): Moving is the best opportunity to get rid of things you no longer use. Check your wardrobe, basement, and attic. Sell, donate, or throw things away. The fewer things you have, the cheaper and faster the move will be.<\/p><p data-path-to-node=\"8\">\u2022 Gather important documentation: Prepare a folder for personal documents, contracts, medical records, and papers related to your new home. Never let this folder out of your hands during the move.<\/p><p data-path-to-node=\"8\">\u2022 Book the logistics: If you are hiring a moving service, now is the time to book a date. If you are moving on your own, check which of your friends can help you with a van or transport.<\/p><p data-path-to-node=\"8\">\u00a0<\/p><p data-path-to-node=\"9\"><strong>3 weeks before the move: Ordering packaging<\/strong><\/p><p data-path-to-node=\"10\">\u2022 Forget about collecting old cardboard boxes: Searching for torn cardboard boxes outside local stores will waste a lot of your time, and in the end, you risk the bottom tearing under the weight of your valuables.<\/p><p data-path-to-node=\"10\">\u2022 Order professional crates: For a safe apartment move, the right moving packaging is key. At Rabimbox, you can easily rent sturdy, plastic crates delivered right to your home. They are clean, waterproof, and stackable on top of each other without any risk of collapsing.<\/p><p data-path-to-node=\"10\">\u00a0<\/p><p data-path-to-node=\"11\"><strong>2 weeks before the move: Systematic packing<\/strong><\/p><p data-path-to-node=\"12\">\u2022 Start with items you don't need every day: Pack seasonal clothes, books, decorative items, and fine dining\/special occasion tableware that you rarely use first.<\/p><p data-path-to-node=\"12\">\u2022 Label each crate: Every Rabimbox crate has a dedicated spot for a label. Clearly write the contents and the destination room (e.g., \"Kitchen \u2013 plates\" or \"Bedroom \u2013 bedding\"). This will save you hours of time when looking for essential items in your new apartment.<\/p><p data-path-to-node=\"12\">\u2022 Use the recipe for safe packing: Place something soft (e.g., a towel) at the bottom of the crate, stack heavier items at the bottom, and lighter, fragile items on top. Fill any empty spaces with paper to prevent the contents from shifting during the drive.<\/p><p data-path-to-node=\"12\">\u00a0<\/p><p data-path-to-node=\"12\"><strong>1 week before the move: Final details<\/strong><\/p><p data-path-to-node=\"14\">\u2022 Prepare a \"first-day suitcase\": Each family member should pack a backpack or a small suitcase with clothes for a few days, basic toiletries, phone chargers, and essential medications. This way, you won't have to open all the crates on your first night in the new home just to find a toothbrush.<\/p><p data-path-to-node=\"14\">\u2022 Defrost the refrigerator and freezer: Consume the remaining food and clean the household appliances in time so they are ready for safe transport.<\/p><p data-path-to-node=\"14\">\u2022 Set up mail forwarding: Inform your bank, electricity provider, and other institutions about your change of address.<\/p><p data-path-to-node=\"14\">\u00a0<\/p><p data-path-to-node=\"15\"><strong>Moving day: Action!<\/strong><\/p><p data-path-to-node=\"16\">\u2022 Vertical stacking: Because Rabimbox crates are designed for stable vertical stacking, you can stack them high on top of each other in a van or car. This will maximize space utilization and reduce the number of trips.<\/p><p data-path-to-node=\"16\">\u2022 Final walkthrough of the premises: Before locking the old doors for the last time, walk through all the rooms once more and check if any forgotten small item is left in a corner.<\/p><p data-path-to-node=\"16\">\u00a0<\/p><p data-path-to-node=\"17\"><strong>Conclusion<\/strong><\/p><p data-path-to-node=\"18\">With good organization and the right tools, moving doesn't have to be a nightmare. If you choose to rent professional crates instead of taping up cardboard boxes, the entire process will be faster, and your items will be safe from impacts and dirt.<\/p><p data-path-to-node=\"18\">\u00a0<\/p><p data-path-to-node=\"19\"><strong>Make your next move simple!<\/strong><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-4139f15 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"4139f15\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-6a3e94bd elementor-button-info elementor-align-center elementor-widget elementor-widget-button\" data-id=\"6a3e94bd\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"button.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-button-wrapper\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<a class=\"elementor-button elementor-button-link elementor-size-sm\" href=\"https:\/\/rabimbox.si\/en\/izposoja\/\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-button-content-wrapper\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-button-text\">Order moving crates<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/a>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-7ff84f86 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"7ff84f86\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-15beeb27 elementor-widget-divider--view-line elementor-widget elementor-widget-divider\" data-id=\"15beeb27\